tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE voice_commands (command_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  command_text VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  user_id INT NOT NULL,
  created_at TIMESTAMP NOT NULL);

CREATE TABLE user_profiles (user_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  username VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  email VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
  date_of_birth DATE);

CREATE TABLE user_preferences (user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  language VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  theme VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  notification_enabled BOOLEAN NOT NULL);

CREATE TABLE user_devices (device_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id INT NOT NULL,
  device_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  os_version VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL);

CREATE TABLE user_profiles (
    user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    first_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    last_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    email VARCHAR(100) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
    birthdate DATE NOT NULL,
    gender CHAR(1) NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE voice_recognition_data (
    data_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    command_id INT NOT NULL,
    user_id INT NOT NULL,
    recognition_result TEXT NOT NULL,
    confidence FLOAT NOT NULL
);
